  Module 8 — Pipeline Automation (08_airflow_pipeline.py)

  

  What: Apache Airflow DAG that runs all 6 steps in sequence every week.



  Architecture:

  ingest → clean → features → train → segment → recommend/forecast

  

  Two delivery options:

  - run_pipeline.py — standalone runner, no Airflow needed, for demo/testing

  - Airflow DAG — production-grade, scheduled, with dependency management

  

  Interview point: "The pipeline means this isn't a one-time analysis. If you drop new transaction data in, the whole system re-runs: features are recomputed, the churn model retrains, segments are refreshed, recommendations are updated. That's what

  makes it a platform, not just a notebook."



